data.description: Incredible opportunity for a custom home on 4.6 acres in the pine trees minutes from Sisters. Traditional style home is 3057 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings and great room ready for entertaining. Chef's kitchen is big with quality appliances, solid countertops, breakfast bar, farm sink, insta hot, custom cabinets and pantry. Home includes dining room, private master suite with peekaboo Cascade Mountain Views, office/utility room, wood stove, sauna and attached garage with apoxy floors. Wonderful outdoor living with covered patio and hot tub in the private back yard. The shop includes: 2 studios with bathrooms, RV storage 50 amp power and full hookups, attached garage, work area and storage. Barn/Equipment storage, 2 containers and woodshed. This home, shop and property has been completely updated, is move in ready and a must see!
